{"tid":1365042,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"（突發）旺角有黑衣女子被圍毆","createTime":"2019-07-25T13:39:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-25T23:42:07.000Z","uid":278443,"like":850,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":134,"replies":[{"pid":"760dcf0a9b32b2e14cbb3803d1d64f2d823ed401","tid":1365042,"uid":278443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T13:39:17.000Z","msg":"6月12日，一名少女被噴中胡椒噴霧痛苦倒地後，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>被至少8個防暴警察對她拳打腳踢，及用警棍、長盾毒打。警暴導致身體多處嚴重瘀傷，險肌肉壞死。</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n毒打片段：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hkpfviolence/videos/600211997170367/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhkpfviolence%2Fvideos%2F600211997170367%2F&d=VlhNwxbPYDbrmmiZclZ9hMeYC5A6rl8%2B6t9FBevN87M%3D&h=ee9ce879\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hkpfviolence/videos/600211997170367/</a><br />\n<br />\n事隔一個月，該少女接受 港台電視部－公共事務組 訪問，指自己事後有極大心理陰影，不斷發惡夢，必須服用安眠藥方可入睡。<br />\n<br />\n鏗鏘集：612/721的傷口（相關訪問）：<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/bcMBmlC855Y?t=385\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FbcMBmlC855Y%3Ft%3D385&d=VlhNwxbPYDbrmmiZclZ9hMeYC5A6rl8%2B6t9FBevN87M%3D&h=f5e5c0d7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/bcMBmlC855Y?t=385</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n然而，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>有關警察至今仍然逍遙法外，不用付上代價</strong></span></span></span>。我們別無他法，人民必須自救，為受警暴折磨的市民報仇。而第一步，就是不斷用各種方法，宣揚黑警暴行。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rzPbRfX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrzPbRfX.png&h=8311e251&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>#毋忘黑警暴行<br />\n#清算香港警賊<br />\n#成立獨立調查委員會<br />\n#撒回逃犯條例<br />\n#平反612暴動定性<br />\n#釋放被捕人士<br />\n#還我真普選<br />\n</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"37bbcd0f1cc9899cfd451c5ef4f2ac0b73be5cb0","tid":1365042,"uid":278443,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T13:44:59.000Z","msg":"認住d黑警"},{"pid":"62aec21db904d69ae9c287ebf832e071b3c54685","tid":1365042,"uid":278443,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T13:45:09.000Z","msg":"認住d黑警"},{"pid":"28aa8e3bfeb7559779188f59a981d3fa084e9ea2","tid":1365042,"uid":278443,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T13:45:19.000Z","msg":"認住d黑警"},{"pid":"b4e427d3435491116750c7b7d97528e6c96db149","tid":1365042,"uid":278443,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T13:45:29.000Z","msg":"認住d黑警"},{"pid":"2972eece48a2c3318154ea1fb662488423d01095","tid":1365042,"uid":278443,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T13:45:39.000Z","msg":"認住d黑警"},{"pid":"283f06e51a99b93f9b56694b2d3ff459f708eb34","tid":1365042,"uid":278443,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T13:45:50.000Z","msg":"認住d黑警"},{"pid":"cef00fcaaf39fe3cf6cb0092f8ead052d6ec8122","tid":1365042,"uid":278443,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T13:46:04.000Z","msg":"清算黑警"},{"pid":"0a41e580eb69e139d073566961dacb5f994e9c25","tid":1365042,"uid":278443,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T13:46:14.000Z","msg":"清算黑警"},{"pid":"7181d468e8bde6f97d5c8fe246768867f3ec2be6","tid":1365042,"uid":278443,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T13:46:24.000Z","msg":"清算黑警"},{"pid":"2c989353f0825f873576ee9dce37c9160d786c07","tid":1365042,"uid":156326,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T13:46:31.000Z","msg":"唔好唔記得 唔好放低憤怒"},{"pid":"e33633e0433e2b26a3adb9700fcbe7e168f71913","tid":1365042,"uid":282494,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T13:46:44.000Z","msg":"原來有D咁既事<br />\n果然是要追究警方過份使用武力"},{"pid":"9b893d2094a271877ff5e1723b7fef92277d434e","tid":1365042,"uid":278443,"like":1,"dislike":0,