13:57:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港警察向黑社會屈服<br />\n打擊香港人遊行集會自由</span></span>"},{"pid":"41318af62f185d4138dbeb69c2f93ece4ed4e0a0","tid":1365042,"uid":261558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T13:58:36.000Z","msg":"好心痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fb5588c1aea688add21283b56d598c03bf5b720","tid":1365042,"uid":125553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T13:58:39.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">仲有612中信事件，警方做法同謀殺無分別，必須成立獨立調查委員會</span></span>"},{"pid":"2350f5c98d420da17c6a5fd55a22b0a55d82fab2","tid":1365042,"uid":28307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T13:59:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd4632dd223510f9168e6b74e54c3789ec91adda","tid":1365042,"uid":158235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T14:10:01.000Z","msg":"濫用暴力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d3e07a198b98f6c1c916c7d4a1b6ce3b70e5f0a","tid":1365042,"uid":18310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T14:18:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"538aa4e5c99694196faab241c0c796188ac62a13","tid":1365042,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T14:18:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3eb319a5c671a1e886faee9a9cc71735eb418db4","tid":1365042,"uid":25598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T14:28:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c1b31759059d514cc5470e58e26745ff6ccee433","tid":1365042,"uid":255659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T14:28:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e7e6c804af2c24a3a93dd4a63007c82d49f6ff89","tid":1365042,"uid":159791,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T14:34:34.000Z","msg":"<pre><code data-type=\"\">各位香港市民及世界各地關心香港的朋友：\n\n我們是一群來自香港民間的示威者。\n由六月初至今，數以百萬計香港人多次以和平、理性、非暴力的方式，包括遊行、集會等，\n向政府，以至全世界表達我們「反送中」的訴求。\n有示威者甚至甘願冒性命危險，背水一戰，短暫進佔立法會；\n除此以外，短短月餘之間已有五位手足不惜捨生取義，以死相諫，試圖喚醒政府僅餘的良知\n及香港人的惻隱之心。\n\n可惜，一切血汗付諸流水，只換來政府的冷眼漠視，以及行政長官一再堅拒撤回「送中惡法」\n的無情回應。\n\n每次和平集會期間，無恥的特區政府均以前線警員為擋箭牌，放任警員以過度武力對付示威者，\n令大量市民受傷流血。與此同時，特首、高官以及一眾建制派議員卻一直躲在背後，拒絕回應\n群眾，妄圖以暴力手段解決政治問題，堅持與民為敵。\n\n今天，我們再一次重申對特區政府的五大訴求：\n\n一、徹底撤回逃犯條例修訂，以達至法理上終止修例程序\n二、收回612暴動定性\n三、撤銷對之前及今後所有反送中抗爭者控罪\n四、成立獨立調查委員會，徹底追究警隊濫權\n五、以行政命令解散立法會，立即實行真正的雙普選\n\n我們熱愛香港，不願再有香港人為守護家園而流血，甚至犠牲寶貴性命。\n但我們強調&mdash;&mdash;「沒有暴民，只有暴政」，\n我們誓必以一切方法迫使政府完全正面回應並實現我們的訴求。\n我們促請政府盡快回心轉意，使香港重回正軌，成為團結、民主、自由、公義的社會。</code></pre><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zfNKZRPQHZk&amp;feature=youtu.be\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DzfNKZRPQHZk%26feature%3Dyoutu.be&d=VlhNwxbPYDbrmmiZclZ9hMeYC5A6rl8%2B6t9FBevN87M%3D&h=1cdd3dc0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zfNKZRPQHZk&amp;feature=youtu.be</a>"},{"pid":"9e939dbecc3c409bda7ce13071bc072312cb9eee","tid":1365042,"uid":835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T14:36:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd87d4a157969b1aeafd357baf15af12cea8dfa5","tid":1365042,"uid":183017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T14:39:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6d13096045a474a0ff6363c5e22e01e26b616135","tid":1365042,"uid":38745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sco