},{"pid":"7e818dccd28a11beab5553ac9f802367ad8dc8fd","tid":1365042,"uid":188035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"760dcf0a9b32b2e14cbb3803d1d64f2d823ed401","tid":1365042,"uid":278443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T13:39:17.000Z","msg":"6月12日，一名少女被噴中胡椒噴霧痛苦倒地後，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>被至少8個防暴警察對她拳打腳踢，及用警棍、長盾毒打。警暴導致身體多處嚴重瘀傷，險肌肉壞死。</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n毒打片段：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hkpfviolence/videos/600211997170367/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhkpfviolence%2Fvideos%2F600211997170367%2F&d=VlhNwxbPYDbrmmiZclZ9hMeYC5A6rl8%2B6t9FBevN87M%3D&h=ee9ce879\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hkpfviolence/videos/600211997170367/</a><br />\n<br />\n事隔一個月，該少女接受 港台電視部－公共事務組 訪問，指自己事後有極大心理陰影，不斷發惡夢，必須服用安眠藥方可入睡。<br />\n<br />\n鏗鏘集：612/721的傷口（相關訪問）：<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/bcMBmlC855Y?t=385\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FbcMBmlC855Y%3Ft%3D385&d=VlhNwxbPYDbrmmiZclZ9hMeYC5A6rl8%2B6t9FBevN87M%3D&h=f5e5c0d7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/bcMBmlC855Y?t=385</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n然而，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>有關警察至今仍然逍遙法外，不用付上代價</strong></span></span></span>。我們別無他法，人民必須自救，為受警暴折磨的市民報仇。而第一步，就是不斷用各種方法，宣揚黑警暴行。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rzPbRfX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrzPbRfX.png&h=8311e251&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>#毋忘黑警暴行<br />\n#清算香港警賊<br />\n#成立獨立調查委員會<br />\n#撒回逃犯條例<br />\n#平反612暴動定性<br />\n#釋放被捕人士<br />\n#還我真普選<br />\n</strong></span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T16:20:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"088398802a67d9824406602eef41be867ead70b2","tid":1365042,"ui