長盡快作出以上各點，這是最後機會；否則，現在全港群情洶湧，後果你要完全負責!</span><br />\n</span></strong>"},{"pid":"1ea37cc39606f582991f762ef1e16419456415d8","tid":1365042,"uid":30850,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T17:15:58.000Z","msg":"推呀！！！"},{"pid":"391d9ac79d489f869ee80a26bd695542297628d4","tid":1365042,"uid":30850,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T17:16:19.000Z","msg":"認撚住每一個"},{"pid":"18007cb1a0e7f44d3c41dcf3baa72cf942f75c50","tid":1365042,"uid":17358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T17:23:34.000Z","msg":"黑警最低武力真係天大笑話"},{"pid":"b03c978ad635f0e85f212b4ff65fc470303e831e","tid":1365042,"uid":143805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T17:32:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"301bfdff67a8ec4552b5228d8453c2b1ca61b948","tid":1365042,"uid":227452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T17:33:43.000Z","msg":"清算黑警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21900bfb182c1a5fa701ebb2da0d93b926a86a5b","tid":1365042,"uid":5131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T17:39:59.000Z","msg":"祝黑警全部生cancer死<br />\n話我係醫護人員都係咁講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c650d55a595810652ca90f2eaa99e484351f7a36","tid":1365042,"uid":79273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T17:41:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fdfbac2f77a9589c851f2f089cc57b85e77b79b7","tid":1365042,"uid":187861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T17:42:39.000Z","msg":"認住呢個極權"},{"pid":"040e23fd817eb7ad9e3b97e4ff9d1c586acb6a2d","tid":1365042,"uid":55932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T17:43:32.000Z","msg":"圍村土生土長，想同大家分析圍村生態同地勢<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1361067\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1361067</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"c21c